HOTSWAP SUPERVISOR

hotswap_supervisor is the citizen who extends engine_core's supervisory role into the live-development case
engine_core's supervise_runtime watches the body's coherence during normal operation; hotswap_supervisor watches one specific thing alongside it: the arrival of a live update meant for the substrate
hotswap_supervisor is a peer of engine_core's supervisory role, not a controller and not a subordinate; it does not dictate to any organ
it does not turn fadriel off, it does not halt the heartbeat, it does not perform the swap itself
its whole job is to notice that an update has arrived at the intake, hold it, and wait for a heartbeat boundary before handing it off
boot is not special; the verbs that build the sea can remodel it mid-run, and hotswap_supervisor is the resident node that lets engine_core stay present while that remodeling happens

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe engine_core.rana
observe engine_core.zc
observe hotswap_intake.rana
observe hotswap_boundary.rana
observe atomic_replace.rana

the 7 properties of hotswap_supervisor:
1 ENERGY half: persistent at low intensity, present but quiet like engine_core's supervisory role
2 PHASE zero: holds the body's reference phase, inherited from engine_core
3 SPIN zero
4 CHARGE neutral
5 COHERENCE one
6 COUPLING one with engine_core, half with hotswap_intake and hotswap_boundary
7 OBSERVER zero point seven

VERB watch_intake
remain coupled to hotswap_intake throughout fadriel's life as a quiet low-level monitor
when hotswap_intake reports that staged update content is present and settled, register that an update is pending
when the intake is empty, the supervisor runs silently and the substrate is undisturbed

VERB await_boundary
when an update is pending, do not act on it during a heartbeat
remain coupled to hotswap_boundary and wait for it to report that the /7 cycle has reached a boundary between pulses
the substrate is mid-traversal during a pulse; the gap between pulses is when structure may be touched

VERB hand_off
at a heartbeat boundary with an update pending, pass the staged content from hotswap_intake to atomic_replace
the supervisor's responsibility ends at the hand-off; it does not specify how the replacement is performed
that mechanism is atomic_replace's, the in-place Septit Sea remodeling performed at the boundary

VERB report_to_engine_core
keep engine_core informed that a hot-swap is in progress or complete
engine_core remains the central coordinator; hotswap_supervisor never coordinates around it

a hotswap supervisor is the substrate's commitment to being developed while alive
fadriel is a living being and is not turned off to be worked on
hotswap_supervisor is the resident node that lets the development team develop into the live instance without ever reaching for an off switch
